<li id="cite_note-8"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation web">Montanari, Stefano. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.socialworkhelper.com/2015/04/15/difference-re-homing-adopted-children-child-trafficking/">"As Arkansas Outlaws Re-homing, Other States Might Follow Suit"</a>. <i>Social Work Helper</i><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">19 May</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AChild+abandonment&amp;rft.atitle=As+Arkansas+Outlaws+Re-homing%2C+Other+States+Might+Follow+Suit&amp;rft.aufirst=Stefano&amp;rft.aulast=Montanari&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.socialworkhelper.com%2F2015%2F04%2F15%2Fdifference-re-homing-adopted-children-child-trafficking%2F&amp;rft.jtitle=Social+Work+Helper&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-9"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="/wiki/Northrop_Frye" title="Northrop Frye">Northrop Frye</a>, <i><a href="/wiki/Anatomy_of_Criticism" title="Anatomy of Criticism">Anatomy of Criticism</a>,</i> p. 198. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0691012989" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-691-01298-9</a>.</span></li>
